OL,3,CPolice called to brawl at Sheffield
OL,4,Cschool
OL,6,FPolice have been called to a school in
OL,7,FSheffield after a fight involving
OL,8,Fstudents.
OL,10,FOfficers responded to a reported
OL,11,Fdisturbance at Fir Vale Academy on
OL,12,FTuesday lunchtime.
OL,14,FClaims that two teachers were taken to
OL,15,Fhospital have not been confirmed.
OL,17,FA number of police cars were pictured
OL,18,Foutside the secondary school, on Owler
OL,19,FLane, on Tuesday afternoon.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
