OL,3,CPolice called to brawl at Sheffield
OL,4,Cschool
OL,6,FA spokesperson for South Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice said: "Shortly after midday
OL,8,Ftoday we were called to reports of a
OL,9,Fdisturbance at Fir Vale Secondary
OL,10,FSchool in Owler Lane, Sheffield.
OL,12,F"It is reported a fight broke out
OL,13,Fbetween a number of students.
OL,15,F"Officers are at the scene and are
OL,16,Fsupporting school staff in the
OL,17,Fresponse."
OL,19,FA spokesperson for Yorkshire Ambulance
OL,20,FService said it was "not aware" of any
OL,21,Fongoing incidents at the school.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
